                        "answer_2": "Our IT consulting services help businesses improve efficiency, enhance security, reduce operational costs, and stay ahead of technology trends. We provide expert guidance to optimize your IT infrastructure and implement innovative solutions.",
                        "is_active": false
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
